## baseline
1.jieba分词
fasttext文本

训练参数：{
    "input": "/data/work/dl_project/data/corpus/thuc_news/train.txt",
    "label": "__label__",
    "epoch": 100,
    "lr": 0.08,
    "lrUpdateRate": 100,
    "minn": 2,
    "maxn": 4,
    "loss": "hs",
    "minCount": 3,
    "wordNgrams": 4,
    "bucket": 2000
}

训练集准确率：
样本数N	336401
精确率P	0.921
召回率R	0.921

验证集准确率：
样本数N	96116
精确率P	0.908
召回率R	0.908

测试集准确率:
样本数N	48060
精确率P	0.905
召回率R	0.905



